<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>蜗牛直播后台</title>
    <meta name="description" content="蜗牛移动">
    <meta name="author" content="woniu" />
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0" name="viewport">
    <meta http-equiv="cleartype" content="on">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon.ico">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/common/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/new_seminar.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css"/>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="wrapper">
		<div class="container container-fluid">
			<div class="header row">
				<div class="col-xs-2">
					<a class="logo" href=""></a>
				</div>
  				<div class="col-xs-7 header-center">
  					<em class="big-font">蜗牛直播</em>
					<em class="little-font">后台管理系统</em>
  				</div>
  				<div class="col-xs-3 header-right">
					<em class="username">陈伟飞</em>
					<em class="erect"> | </em>
					<a class="login-out" href="">退出</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="main">
				<div class="login-bar">
					<a href="javascript:history.go(-1)" class="login-bar-left"></a>
					<div class="login-bar-right">专题修改</div>
				</div>
                <form action="/addSpecial" method="post">
				<div class="sem-area">
					<div class="sem_select">
						<div class="col-xs-4">
							<div class="sem-font pull-right">所属项目：</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-xs-8">
							<select name="category_id">
                                <% for(var i=0;i<cates.length;i++){ %>
                                <option value="<%= cates[i]._id%>"><%= cates[i].title %></option>
                                <%}%>
							</select>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-name">
						<div class="col-xs-4">
							<div class="sem-font pull-right">项目名称：</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-xs-8">
							<div class="sem-inp">
								<input type="text" name="title"/>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="col-code">
						<div class="col-xs-4">
							<div class="sem-font pull-right">项目代码：</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-xs-8">
							<div class="sem-inp">
								<input type="text" name="special_code"/>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="col-msg">
						 * 专题代码全部用小写英文字母、数字、下划线的组合，其中不得包含汉字、空格和特殊字符；专题代码应以英文为主（不到万不得已不要以拼音作为名称），如2014CJ直播专题命名为cj2014,2014年中国杯帆船赛命名为2014chncup等。专题代码、所属栏目务必慎重填写，专题一经生成不可更改。自动生成专题链接live.snail.com/B/A.html  A即为此处填入的代码。
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="sem-btn">
					<div class="col-xs-6">
						<a href="" class="show-btn btn-cancel">取 消</a>
					</div>
					<div class="col-xs-6">
						<button type="submit" class="show-btn btn-publish">发 布</button>
					</div>
				</div>
                </form>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

<script type="text/javascript" src="/js/jquery-1.10.2.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/common/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/js/index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>